<p> Courts (law) </p>

<p> Drug treatment </p>

<p> Federal grants </p>

<p> Defendants </p>

<p> Drug abuse </p>

<p> Law enforcement </p>

<p> Recidivism </p>

<p> Offender rehabilitation </p>

<p> IDENTIFIER: Dade County (FL) </p>

<p> DOJ Corrections Options Program </p>

<p> Federal Drug Court Grant Program </p>

